    545          /***************************************************************************//**
    546           * @brief
    547           *   Initialize the TEMP driver.
    548           *
    549           * @details
    550           *   This will clear all the registered callbacks and enable the EMU IRQ in the
    551           *   NVIC. Calling this function will also enable the EMU_E201 errata fix for
    552           *   first generation Pearl, Jade and EFR32 devices.
    553           *
    554           * @return
    555           *   @ref ECODE_EMDRV_TEMPDRV_OK on success.
    556           ******************************************************************************/

