    729           *
    730           *   @li @ref ECODE_EMDRV_TEMPDRV_PARAM_ERROR if the callback is NULL.
    731           *
    732           *   @li @ref ECODE_EMDRV_TEMPDRV_NO_INIT if the user has forgot to call @ref
