    734           *
    735           *   @li @ref ECODE_EMDRV_TEMPDRV_BAD_LIMIT is returned if \p temp is below the
    736           *     current temperature and \p limit is @ref TEMPDRV_LIMIT_LOW. It is also
    737           *     returned if \p temp is above the current temperature and \p limit is
